The Palo Alto community is sharing its memories of Palo Alto High School science teacher Kenyon Scott, <a href="http://palyvoice.com/2016/01/07/community-mourns-teacher-death/">who died of unidentified natural causes on Jan. 6 in his home.</a> Photos by William Zhou, Bianca Al-Shamari, Sam Lee and Takaaki Sagawa.

